{"tid":434712,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有家姐真係好煩","createTime":"2017-10-13T14:29:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-30T00:38:31.000Z","uid":126137,"like":14,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"14e430093d76328c895a60c5e6e2f8a4493bc6e1","tid":434712,"uid":126137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T14:29:55.000Z","msg":"細細個已經成日威脅我<br />\n唔幫佢做呢樣個樣就會block咗電腦唔比我用<br />\n我疑似係咁所以大個咗變得細膽<br />\n到大個啲會share衫、鞋嗰啲<br />\n你話小學、中學都share無問題<br />\n但人大咗 你就開始會有佔有欲<br />\n有啲衫、鞋唔想借<br />\n所以佢都講:我用你啲嘢你會唔開心 我都係<br />\n從此 我都無唔問過佢就用佢嘅野<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啱啱佢返屋企 比我見到佢未問過我就著我對鞋<br />\n仲要污糟咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我話你要洗返好<br />\n佢就話唔係佢整污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我心諗我最尾一次着都冇呢撻污跡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同佢噪就搬返哂以前啲嘢講<br />\n又話要將心比己 都最後又咁仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有家姐都知 <br />\n佢好可以好好<br />\n不過仆街可以係最仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n尊重兩個字識唔識寫啊</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正評：同病相連<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 負評：做細就係咁 樓主抵死"},{"pid":"16c21f5fc290aa50633933767bbe05addee2ef88","tid":434712,"uid":127272,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T14:30:46.000Z","msg":"吾要送畀me<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45094dd1217f768f668206f849a760979e7d7582","tid":434712,"uid":126137,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T14:34:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吾要送畀me<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">吾你老母啊 5p狗<br />\n死撚返去5p啦<br />\n送你入5p啊</span>"},{"pid":"750537b58af2d166f3cdd9e438b6632991578d60","tid":434712,"uid":43621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T14:35:42.000Z","msg":"Agree <br />\n利申 家姐係控制狂 做咩都管"},{"pid":"2831c6be3f380e5ee1820af11b68a34603e4cbc7","tid":434712,"uid":99344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T14:36:11.000Z","msg":"我家姐唔會 係有時會好燥底 唔燥底嗰陣對我都幾好"},{"pid":"3beeb170472ae1317b624703d41f972a17285a38","tid":434712,"uid":126137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T14:38:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Agree <br />\n利申 家姐係控制狂 做咩都管</blockquote><br />\n你到18歲佢都管你？<br />\n咁就唔得喎巴打 自由都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無話佢最過分管你啲咩？"},{"pid":"378e62a4bec74dc51371d1cdda3bc81a5e51cf6c","tid":434712,"uid":81234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T14:39:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5831f99f7e8cf8409d4e4f60505eef7bf13fde49","tid":434712,"uid":126137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T14:40:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我家姐唔會 係有時會好燥底 唔燥底嗰陣對我都幾好</blockquote><br />\n我家姐都係 唔燥地可以講下心事<br />\n但一燥底就反轉豬肚就係屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4e35af725b09f78cea562c6698311e477897dce","t